flowchart TD
    A([Entry]) --> B[Def interval parameter]
    B --> C[Def interval via getReadableInterval(interval)]
    C --> D[P-use interval in overlaps(interval)]
    D --> E{overlaps false?}
    E -- Yes --> F[Return null]
    E -- No --> G[Def start=max(thisStart, otherStart)]
    G --> H[Def end=min(thisEnd, otherEnd)]
    H --> I[C-use start,end in new Interval(start,end,...)]
    I --> J([Exit])
    F --> J
